$interpreted: Slums Man: How did this happen? First Phil, now Mr. Eugene...
Slums Woman: It has to be "that", right? The Ragdoll Coroner...
Lio: What happened?
Leah: Let's go and see what the fuss is about!
Lio: Mr. Eugene? How come?
Hyacinthus: I am sorry.
Lio: What are you going to do?
Leah: I'm going to find Nigel and get to the bottom of this! What else?
Leah: What did you do!
Nigel: What do you mean?
Leah: Stop playing dumb! A body just got carried into the Slums. As the "leader" of the Slums, no way in hell would you not know about it!
Nigel: Oh, so you're talking about Eugene...after interrogating him yesterday, I let him go.
Nigel: Who knew he would get caught up in something like this.
Leah: Last night you were with him all by yourself, today he's dead. If it's not you, who else could it be?
Nigel: Stop poking your nose into other people's business. You have Lio, and you have yourself. That's plenty enough for you to worry about!
Leah: Where do you think you're going!?
Nigel: Work. Even though Eugene is dead, doesn't mean that we can abandon our work at the dye workshop.
Leah: Lio, what's your opinion on this?
Lio: I don't think Nigel will lie about this.  Maybe it really was the Ragdoll Coroner who did it?
Leah: Are you stupid? The Ragdoll Coroner doesn't exist! Didn't you see Eugene wearing that mask!?
Lio: But...
Leah: Believe me, you can't trust Nigel!
Leah: Come, let's go to work! I'll keep my eye on Nigel every single second. I dare him to do something bad again!
Lio: Looks like I have to prove Nigel's innocence...
Leah: What are you wandering around for?
Lio: C-Coming!
Lio: It really is creepy here at night...
Lio: No, I can't be scared! I must prove that Nigel was wronged!
Lio: What's that noise!?
Lio: What is this? It's so pretty!
Lio: It can fly!?
Lio: Is it a toy? I'll call you Flutterfly from now on. Flutterfly, can you lead the way for me?
Lio: G-Get off me!
Lio: Ugh, so gross...these monster, do they have something to do with the Ragdoll Coroner?
Lio: NO! Can't back down now. I should investigate.
？？？: Broke my doll; you are a bad ~ kid~
